								</h3>
								<div>
									<p class='mx-1 text-sm'>Tech Stack:</p>
									<div class='flex
										flex-wrap'>
										<span class='tech-stack'>Astro</span>
										<span class='tech-stack'
											>TailwindCSS</span
										>
										<span class='tech-stack'>pnpm</span>
